  doctrineandcovenants,29,5,"Lift up your hearts and be glad, for I am in your midst, and am your advocate with the Father; and it is his good will to give you the kingdom.","27:31:Rom. 8:35 (35–39).|50:55:Matt. 18:20; D&C 6:32; 38:7; 88:63 (62–63).|69:77:TG Jesus Christ, Advocate; Jesus Christ, Relationships with the Father.|135:142:Luke 12:31 (22–34); D&C 35:27. TG Kingdom of God, on Earth."
