  doctrineandcovenants,29,17,"And it shall come to pass, because of the wickedness of the world, that I will take vengeance upon the wicked, for they will not repent; for the cup of mine indignation is full; for behold, my blood shall not cleanse them if they hear me not.","84:93:Ps. 73:17 (3–17); Rev. 16:9–11; 2 Ne. 30:10; JS—M 1:55. TG God, Justice of; Vengeance.|103:109:TG Wickedness.|145:148:Jer. 25:15.|157:168:TG God, Indignation of.|193:198:1 Jn. 1:7; Alma 11:40 (40–41); D&C 19:17 (16–18).|209:216:TG Purification."
  doctrineandcovenants,29,18,"Wherefore, I the Lord God will send forth flies upon the face of the earth, which shall take hold of the inhabitants thereof, and shall eat their flesh, and shall cause maggots to come in upon them;","42:47:TG Plague."
  doctrineandcovenants,29,19,"And their tongues shall be stayed that they shall not utter against me; and their flesh shall fall from off their bones, and their eyes from their sockets;","54:59:Ex. 16:8; Zech. 14:12; Rev. 16:9 (9, 11, 21); 1 Ne. 16:22 (20–25)."
  doctrineandcovenants,29,20,And it shall come to pass that the beasts of the forest and the fowls of the air shall devour them up.,"35:41:Isa. 18:6; Jer. 15:3; Ezek. 39:17 (17–20); Rev. 19:17 (17–18)."
  doctrineandcovenants,29,21,"And the great and abominable church, which is the whore of all the earth, shall be cast down by devouring fire, according as it is spoken by the mouth of Ezekiel the prophet, who spoke of these things, which have not come to pass but surely must, as I live, for abominations shall not reign.","18:28:TG Devil, Church of.|50:55:Rev. 19:2. TG Whore.|96:110:Ezek. 38:22; Joel 1:19 (19–20); 2:3; D&C 45:41 (40–41); 97:26 (25–26). TG Earth, Cleansing of.|241:245:D&C 1:38.|262:274:Ezek. 5:9 (9–11)."
  doctrineandcovenants,29,22,"And again, verily, verily, I say unto you that when the thousand years are ended, and men again begin to deny their God, then will I spare the earth but for a little season;","56:64:TG Millennium.|159:172:Rev. 20:3 (3–10); Jacob 5:77 (76–77); D&C 43:31 (30–31); 88:111 (110–12)."
  doctrineandcovenants,29,23,"And the end shall come, and the heaven and the earth shall be consumed and pass away, and there shall be a new heaven and a new earth.","8:11:Matt. 24:14. TG Earth, Destiny of; World, End of.|75:84:Matt. 24:35; JS—M 1:35.|124:133:TG Earth, Renewal of."
