  doctrineandcovenants,33,3,"For behold, the field is white already to harvest; and it is the eleventh hour, and the last time that I shall call laborers into my vineyard.","16:21:John 4:35.|25:30:D&C 4:4; 12:3; 14:3; 101:64.|65:73:Matt. 20:6 (1–16).|116:124:Jacob 5:71 (71–75); D&C 43:28."
  doctrineandcovenants,33,4,"And my vineyard has become corrupted every whit; and there is none which doeth good save it be a few; and they err in many instances because of priestcrafts, all having corrupt minds.","7:15:TG Vineyard of the Lord.|27:36:2 Ne. 28:11 (2–14); Morm. 8:28 (28–41); D&C 38:11.|79:83:Eccl. 7:20; Jer. 13:23; Rom. 3:12; D&C 35:12.|111:114:2 Ne. 27:35 (34–35); 28:14.|144:156:TG Priestcraft."
  doctrineandcovenants,33,5,"And verily, verily, I say unto you, that this church have I established and called forth out of the wilderness.","46:52:TG Church; Jesus Christ, Head of the Church.|60:71:TG Mission of Latter-day Saints.|100:110:Rev. 12:6 (1–6)."
