  doctrineandcovenants,45,4,"Saying: Father, behold the sufferings and death of him who did no sin, in whom thou wast well pleased; behold the blood of thy Son which was shed, the blood of him whom thou gavest that thyself might be glorified;","27:37:TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through; Jesus Christ, Redeemer; Pain; Suffering.|42:47:TG Jesus Christ, Death of.|66:69:Heb. 4:15; 7:26.|203:212:John 12:28."
