  doctrineandcovenants,45,26,"And in that day shall be heard of wars and rumors of wars, and the whole earth shall be in commotion, and men's hearts shall fail them, and they shall say that Christ delayeth his coming until the end of the earth.","7:15:TG Day of the Lord.|34:38:D&C 63:33; 87:1 (1–8); 88:91; JS—M 1:23.|125:129:Luke 21:26.|167:175:Matt. 24:48; 2 Pet. 3:4 (3–10); JS—M 1:51."
  doctrineandcovenants,45,27,"And the love of men shall wax cold, and iniquity shall abound.","8:12:JS—M 1:10.|40:48:Matt. 24:12."
